==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: maiden aunt
<hw>maiden aunt</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Literally, an aunt who has never
been married. Figuratively, it is a term used as the prototype of a
person who is broadly naive and not wise in worldly ways; <as>as, he
knows as much about programming as my <ex>maiden
aunt</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>maiden blue-eyed mary</ent>⟦br⟧
